de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.clustering.pairsegments

Class Segment

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.clustering.pairsegments.Segment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Segment>

    public class Segment
extends Object
implements Comparable<Segment>
    A segment represents a set of pairs that share the same clustering properties. As such, for each ring (= clustering), a cluster number (or the constant UNCLUSTERED) is stored.
    Since:
    0.5.0
    Author:
    Sascha Goldhofer, Erich Schubert
